Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/petere/plxslt

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-plxslt
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-plxslt
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libxslt1.1
Description: Procedural language handler for XSLT in PostgreSQL
  PL/XSLT is a PostgreSQL procedural language that allows writing stored
  procedures directly in XSLT. The first parameter is treated as an XML
  input document, and subsequent parameters become XSL parameters. The
  return type must match the stylesheet output method (xml, text, or html).
